 goats’ hair,","year":-1491},{"id":"recLJ2fldq91RNjPW","ref":"Exod.25.5","text":"And rams’ skins dyed red, and badgers’ skins, and shittim wood,","year":-1491},{"id":"recAB6dLWzCucjEOG","ref":"Exod.25.6","text":"Oil for the light, spices for anointing oil, and for sweet incense,","year":-1491},{"id":"recGmr6uhhDzBvIUN","ref":"Exod.25.7","text":"Onyx stones, and stones to be set in the ephod, and in the breastplate.","year":-1491},{"id":"recdzIUQ1Bm1v4Wyx","ref":"Exod.25.8","text":"And let them make me a sanctuary; that I may dwell among them.","year":-1491}]}
